comments: Brown (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Burks's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Paschall (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Brown's (BOS) drive.
Theis (BOS) sets the screen on Bowman (GSW) and absorbs the contact.
Green (GSW) initiates contact with Theis (BOS) and affects his ability to land after receiving the pass.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) and Smart (BOS) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Paschall (GSW) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Tatum's (BOS) off arm and does not affect his dunk attempt.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) sets the screen on Brown (BOS) and absorbs the contact.
Theis (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during Burks's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Burks (GSW) makes marginal contact with Theis (BOS) following the screen.
Brown (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position on Paschall (GSW) in the post before Paschall has the ball stripped.
Green (GSW) makes contact with the ball and Theis's (BOS) hand which is part of the ball while defending the shot attempt.
Green (GSW) sets the screen on Brown (BOS) and absorbs the contact.
Poole (GSW) initiates contact with Brown (BOS) that dislodges him from his position.
Theis (BOS) sets the screen on Bowman (GSW) and absorbs the contact.
Bowman (GSW) initiates marginal contact with Walker (BOS) and does not affect his FOM.
Green (GSW) initiates contact with Walker (BOS) and affects his SQBR.
